---
title: Lemon-Pepper Pork Chops with Glazed Veggies and Savoury Pan Sauce
description: Winner winner, pork chop dinner!  The bright flavours of lemon and garlic pork chops are balanced by herby rice and aromatic glazed veggies. A quick and delicious pan sauce ties it all together.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/lemon-pepper-pork-chops-eee5559c.jpg
